      "rdfs:label": "Logarithmic Scaling Pattern (Photographic Stops)",
      "rdfs:comment": "Parameters scaled logarithmically (doubling/halving) to match human perception. Each 'stop' represents 2Ãƒâ€” change in physical quantity but equal perceptual step.",
      "m1:principle": "Weber-Fechner Law: Perceived intensity Ã¢Ë†Â log(stimulus)",
